"title": "1409: dream",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1409: dream",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A series of images or thoughts experienced in one's mind while asleep. A means by which a divine message may be conveyed while the recipient sleeps. God may communicate directly in the dream, or interpretation may be necessary.</p>\n<h2>Direct communication through dreams</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:24\">GEN 31:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:3\">GEN 20:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:6\">GEN 20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:6\">1SA 28:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:15\">1SA 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:5\">1KI 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:15\">1KI 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:14-Job33:15\">JOB 33:14–33:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:20\">MAT 1:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:12-Matt2:13\">MAT 2:12–2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:19-Matt2:20\">MAT 2:19–2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:22\">MAT 2:22</a></p>\n<h2>Dreams involving unusual images</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:12-Gen28:15\">GEN 28:12–28:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:10-Gen31:13\">GEN 31:10–31:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:5-Gen37:7\">GEN 37:5–37:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:9\">GEN 37:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:9-Gen40:11\">GEN 40:9–40:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:16-Gen40:17\">GEN 40:16–40:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:1-Gen41:7\">GEN 41:1–41:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:13\">JDG 7:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:31-Dan2:35\">DAN 2:31–2:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:10-Dan4:17\">DAN 4:10–4:17</a></p>\n<h2>God is the source of interpretation of such dreams</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:26-Dan2:28\">DAN 2:26–2:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:8\">GEN 40:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:15-Gen41:16\">GEN 41:15–41:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:25\">GEN 41:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:28\">GEN 41:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:24\">DAN 4:24</a></p>\n<h2>Interpretation of unusual images</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:12-Gen40:13\">GEN 40:12–40:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:18-Gen40:19\">GEN 40:18–40:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:26-Gen41:31\">GEN 41:26–41:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg7:14-Judg7:15\">JDG 7:14–7:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:28\">JER 23:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:23-Jer31:26\">JER 31:23–31:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:36-Dan2:45\">DAN 2:36–2:45</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:19-Dan4:26\">DAN 4:19–4:26</a></p>\n<h2>Revelation to prophets through dreams</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:6\">NUM 12:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28\">JOL 2:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:17\">DAN 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:19-Dan2:23\">DAN 2:19–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:17\">ACT 2:17</a></p>\n<h2>Dreams and false prophets</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:1-Deut13:3\">DEU 13:1–13:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:5\">DEU 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:25-Jer23:27\">JER 23:25–23:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:32\">JER 23:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer27:9\">JER 27:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer29:8-Jer29:9\">JER 29:8–29:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:2\">ZEC 10:2</a></p>\n<h2>Ordinary dreams</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:7-Isa29:8\">ISA 29:7–29:8</a></strong> <em>Not every dream is a vehicle for divine communication.  Most are part of the natural process of sleep.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:13-Job7:15\">JOB 7:13–7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:20\">PSA 73:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:3\">ECC 5:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:7\">ECC 5:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:10\">ISA 56:10</a></p>",
